Why is it that you only get 120, I was hoping to grab one of the emotes, and playing the last event you could grab at least an emote, maybe a champ shard and some b.e.. Are there going to be any more missions to earn tokens when the new content is added to the store?

(Seriously, I don't pay for lol stuff and I like the fact you can earn skins and emotes and such with or without lol specials coming around. Is riot phasing out the viability of grinding the missions to boost ticket sales or am I just missing information ?)

